---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AboutBG from '../images/AboutBG.png';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- ====== Hero ====== -->
  <section class="relative flex min-h-[60vh] items-center overflow-hidden lg:min-h-[70vh]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src={AboutBG.src}
        alt="OLLI members in community"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover blur-sm scale-110"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#02275A]/90 via-[#02275A]/70 to-[#02275A]/45"></div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 h-[500px] w-[800px] max-w-full opacity-[0.2]" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at center, #004ADD 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pb-16 pt-24 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-blue-200 font-semibold mb-4">About Osher</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold font-display text-white leading-tight" style="text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        Championing lifelong learning for adults 50 and better
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        The Bernard Osher Foundation has supported a national network of Osher Lifelong Learning Institutes for more than four decades. OLLI at Hampton University brings that legacy to Hampton Roads with affordable, community-driven programming designed to enrich every stage of life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Curved bottom separator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-10 h-16">
      <svg class="h-full w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 64" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="#FFFFFF">
        <path d="M0 64 Q360 0 720 32 Q1080 64 1440 16 L1440 64 Z" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.7fr_1fr] items-start">
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-[#F8FAFC] p-10 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#004ADD]/30 mb-4"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold font-display text-[#02275A] mb-4">OLLI at Hampton University</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
            OLLI at Hampton furthers the pursuit of lifelong learning by offering affordable, accessible, high-quality educational programs for the population 50 and better in the Hampton Roads area.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
            Programs are conducted in an environment that fosters members’ participation in the planning, execution, and assessment of all programs. OLLI broadens and enriches the lives of its members by challenging intellectual activities that stimulate creativity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-[#F8FAFC] p-10 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#004ADD]/30 mb-4"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold font-display text-[#02275A] mb-4">A nationwide lifelong learning network</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
            The Foundation supports a national lifelong learning network of programs designed for adults 50 and better; Osher Lifelong Learning Institutes operate on 120+ college and university campuses in all 50 states and the District of Columbia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-[#F8FAFC] p-10 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#004ADD]/30 mb-4"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold font-display text-[#02275A] mb-4">A foundation built for impact</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
            Bernard Osher Foundation, headquartered in San Francisco, was founded in 1977 by respected businessman, philanthropist, and community leader Bernard Osher. The Foundation seeks to improve quality of life through innovative funding in higher education and the arts.
          </p>
        </div>      </div>

      <aside class="space-y-8">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-[#02275A] p-10 text-white shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-[#93C5FD]">Osher Institute Legacy</p>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold font-display">Watch the story</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#DDE8FF]">
            View a brief animated video history of The Osher Institute Legacy of Bernard Osher.
          </p>
          <a href="https://vimeo.com/873071530?share=copy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full mt-8 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-center text-[#02275A] font-semibold shadow-lg hover:bg-[#F3F8FC] transition">
            Watch the Video
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A] mb-3">Why OLLI?</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700">
            <li><strong class="font-semibold">Accessible</strong> programs with no grades, no tests, and no homework.</li>
            <li><strong class="font-semibold">Member-led</strong> learning shaped by the interests of the community.</li>
            <li><strong class="font-semibold">Engaging</strong> courses, travel, and social activities for lifelong learners.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#004ADD] font-bold mb-4">Learn More</p>
          <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <a href="https://www.osherfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#004ADD] px-6 py-4 text-center text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-[#02275A] transition">
              Osher Foundation
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.hamptonu.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#004ADD] px-6 py-4 text-center text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-[#02275A] transition">
              Hampton University
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
